data.description: **Seller Financing Option with rates as low as 3.875% Two-story stunner! This gorgeous one-of-a-kind 5 bedroom, 3 full bathroom home sits at the end of a quiet culdesac with mature trees and a private lot. Recently renovated, you'll enter a large formal sitting and dining area that opens to a family room and a large open kitchen with extensive cabinets.  The main floor also features a bedroom and a full bathroom, perfect for a guest suite.  Upstairs you'll enjoy a loft area, followed by the primary bedroom with an ensuite bathroom and an ample closet with custom shelving.  You'll also find 2 additional bedrooms and a large bathroom.   Outside, you'll find mature trees, a large corner lot, and an oversized covered patio, perfect for entertaining.  This home is close to HWY 1604 and HWY 10 and near an abundance of shopping.
